ecause the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" came down on it in fire. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 3:2","book":"Exo","chapter":3,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 24:17","book":"Exo","chapter":24,"verse":17,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 4:11","book":"Deu","chapter":4,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Ch 7:1","book":"2Ch","chapter":7,"verse":1,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" Its smoke went up like the smoke of a furnace, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 144:5","book":"Psa","chapter":144,"verse":5,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 15:8","book":"Rev","chapter":15,"verse":8,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" and the whole mountain shook violently. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jdg 5:5","book":"Jdg","chapter":5,"verse":5,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 68:7","book":"Psa","chapter":68,"verse":7,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 4:24","book":"Jer","chapter":4,"verse":24,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 12:26","book":"Heb","chapter":12,"verse":26,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 3:2","book":"Exo","chapter":3,"verse":2},{"label":"Ex 24:17","book":"Exo","chapter":24,"verse":17},{"label":"Dt 4:11","book":"Deu","chapter":4,"verse":11},{"label":"2Ch 7:1","book":"2Ch","chapter":7,"verse":1},{"label":"Ps 144:5","book":"Psa","chapter":144,"verse":5},{"label":"Rv 15:8","book":"Rev","chapter":15,"verse":8},{"label":"Jdg 5:5","book":"Jdg","chapter":5,"verse":5},{"label":"Ps 68:7","book":"Psa","chapter":68,"verse":7},{"label":"Jr 4:24","book":"Jer","chapter":4,"verse":24},{"label":"Heb 12:26","book":"Heb","chapter":12,"verse":26}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Exo:19:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"As the sound of the ram’s horn grew louder and louder, Moses spoke and God answered him in the thunder. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Neh 9:13","book":"Neh","chapter":9,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 81:7","book":"Psa","chapter":81,"verse":7,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Neh 9:13","book":"Neh","chapter":9,"verse":13},{"label":"Ps 81:7","book":"Psa","chapter":81,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Exo:19:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" came down on Mount Sinai at the top of the mountain. Then the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" summoned Moses to the top of the mountain, and he went up. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Exo:19:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" directed Moses, “Go down and warn the people not to break through to see the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"; otherwise many of them will die. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 3:5","book":"Exo","chapter":3,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 6:19","book":"1Sa","chapter":6,"verse":19,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 3:5","book":"Exo","chapter":3,"verse":5},{"label":"1Sm 6:19","book":"1Sa","chapter":6,"verse":19}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Exo:19:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Even the priests who come near the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" must consecrate themselves, or the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" will break out in anger against them.” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 10:3","book":"Lev","chapter":10,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Sm 6:7","book":"2Sa","chapter":6,"verse":7,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 10:3","book":"Lev","chapter":10,"verse":3},{"label":"2Sm 6:7","book":"2Sa","chapter":6,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Exo:19:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Moses responded to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":", “The people cannot come up Mount Sinai, since you warned us: Put a boundary around the mountain and consecrate it.” "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Exo:19:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" replied to him, “Go down and come back with Aaron. But the priests and the people must not break through to come up to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":", or he will break out in anger against them.” "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Exo:19:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So Moses went down to the people and told them."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783279322068}